<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<!DOCTYPE mapper
        PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN"
        "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd">
<!--
这里的包名需要指定到类名，否则在使用接口的时候会报错：
org.apache.ibatis.binding.BindingException: Invalid bound statement (not found):
但是不会影响使用sqlSession，为了保证接口能正常使用在此处的namespace需要指定到全类名，
写成这样：
org.cooze.spring.boot.mybatis.xml.mapper.school.SchoolMapper
-->
<mapper namespace="org.cooze.spring.boot.mybatis.mapper.school.SchoolMapper">

    <select id="findBySchoolName" resultType="org.cooze.spring.boot.mybatis.domain.School">
        SELECT * FROM school WHERE name LIKE CONCAT('%',#{name},'%')
    </select>

</mapper>